errormessage.desc_en: Service warning; Make a service maintenance, press back key to clear warning.

errormessage.desc_zh: 交流掉电。掉电或正常关机。
errormessage.desc_en: Power supply is switching off; Power off.

errormessage.desc_zh: 交流过压。检查电源电压。
errormessage.desc_en: AC power supply voltage is too high; Check the ac input.

errormessage.desc_zh: 母线过压。检查电源电压；泄放电路故障；更换泄放电阻。
errormessage.desc_en: Bus voltage is too high; Check the brake circuit, Replace the brake resistor.

errormessage.desc_zh: 电机母线过流。检查编码器接线；更换控制箱。
errormessage.desc_en: The bus current is too high; Check the motor encoder connection; Replace the controlbox.

errormessage.desc_zh: 电机堵转。检查机头是否卡死；缝料厚度超出了机器最大穿刺能力。
errormessage.desc_en: Overload; The speed of main motor is lower than  20rpm; The shaft is blocked; The material is too thick.

errormessage.desc_zh: 电机相电流过流。检查机头是否卡死；缝料厚度超出了机器最大穿刺能力。
errormessage.desc_en: Overload; The current command of main motor exceeds the maximum value.;The shaft is blocked; The material is too thick.

errormessage.desc_zh: 电机启动失败。检查机头是否卡死；缝料厚度超出了机器最大穿刺能力。
errormessage.desc_en: The main motor starts failed; The shaft is blocked; The material is too thick.

errormessage.desc_zh: 电机同步信号丢失。检查针位检测器信号。
errormessage.desc_en: The synchronizer signal is not detected; Check the synchronizaer signal. The shaft is blocked; The material is too thick.

errormessage.desc_zh: 电机霍尔信号。检查UVW信号是否正常。
errormessage.desc_en: Check the UVW signal; Check the hall sensor.

errormessage.desc_zh: 电机上针位同步信号错误。检查针位检测器信号。
errormessage.desc_en: Check the synchronizaer signal. Check the hall sensor.

errormessage.desc_zh: 电磁铁/阀过流。检查电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid.

errormessage.desc_zh: 剪线电磁铁/阀过流。检查剪线电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The trimmer solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 倒缝电磁铁/阀过流。检查倒缝电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The reverse solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 扫线电磁铁/阀过流。检查扫线电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The wiper solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 压脚电磁铁/阀过流。检查压脚电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The foot solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 面线张力电磁铁/阀过流。检查松线电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The main tension solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 电子夹线电磁铁/阀过流。检查夹线电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The  clamp tension solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 大小针距电磁铁/阀过流。检查第二针距电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The small stitch length solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 压脚交互量电磁铁/阀过流。检查抬压脚电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The stroke solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 第二夹线器电磁铁/阀过流。检查第二夹线器电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The second tension solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 分缝压脚电磁铁/阀过流。检查分缝导向电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The part foot solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 机针冷却电磁铁/阀过流。检查机针冷却电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The needle cooling solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 短线头电磁铁/阀过流。检查短线头电磁铁/阀是否短路。
errormessage.desc_en: The short thread trimming solenoid current is too high; Check the solenoid is shorted or not.

errormessage.desc_zh: 同步参数校验失败。重新上电。
errormessage.desc_en: The paramter synchronization is failed; Restart the control box.

errormessage.desc_zh: 特殊模式下操作盒发生重连现象。重新上电。
errormessage.desc_en: The panel is reconnected when some special mode; Restart the controlbox.

errormessage.desc_zh: 参数值超过了上下限。重新上电。
errormessage.desc_en: Parameters verified failed; Restart the controlbox.

errormessage.desc_zh: 步进电机通讯超时。重新上电；检查驱动板之间通信电缆。
errormessage.desc_en: The step drive communication failed; Restart the controlbox. Check the communication cable.

errormessage.desc_zh: 同步参数版本校验失败。升级控制箱或屏幕软件。
errormessage.desc_en: Parameters version verified failed; Update the software of controlbox or panel.

将手轮慢慢旋转，未同步前显示'---'；经过同步点后显示数值为机器角度；在针杆或挑线杆最高处点击确定，显示数值变为0或上针位角度值；基准点设定完成。
panelstrings.desc_en: Turn the handwheel slowly. After the synchronization point, the panel displays the machine angle. Turn to the point which the needle bar or take-up lever is at the highest position. Click 'OK' to save the new base point. The display changes to 0 or up position of needlebar. The setting is finished.

panelstrings.desc_zh: 通过针距电机的移动调整，使缝纫机针距为0，点击确定保存零点位置。
panelstrings.desc_en: Move the stitch length motor to the 0 positon, click 'OK' to save the position.

panelstrings.desc_zh: 1：将交互量拨盘拨至最小挡位，点击下一步。
panelstrings.desc_en: 1. Adjust the stroke knob to the minimum, click the next button

panelstrings.desc_zh: 2：将交互量拨盘拨至最大挡位，点击下一步，完成电位器校准。
panelstrings.desc_en: 2. Adjust the stroke knob to the maximum, click the next button to complete the calibration.
Copy sewing stitches program from machine to usbstick

panelstrings.desc_zh: 将U盘里的缝纫数据拷贝至缝纫机
panelstrings.desc_en: Copy sewing stitches program from usbstick to machine
Copy parameters from machine to usbstick

panelstrings.desc_zh: 将U盘里的参数数据拷贝至缝纫机
panelstrings.desc_en: Copy parameters from usb stick to machine

panelstrings.desc_zh: 正常的电机电角度应从0度变化至360度，依次循环，每次增加值为60度，否则电机存在故障。
panelstrings.desc_en: If the motor is normal, the electrical angle changes from 0 to 360, each step incremental is 60. Otherwise the motor is not normal.

panelstrings.desc_zh: 恢复出厂值与机器型号相关，请确保机器型号设置正确；选择一项点击重置键后关机再开机即可恢复出厂值。
panelstrings.desc_en: The factory default value is related to the machine model. Please make sure the machine model is set correctly. Select an item and click the 'Reset' button, then restart the control box to make a factory reset.

panelstrings.desc_zh: 1：松掉脚踏，确认脚踏处于平衡位置(0)，点击下一步。
panelstrings.desc_en: 1. Release the pedal and confirm that the pedal is in the balance position (0), click Next.

panelstrings.desc_zh: 2：将脚踏正踩到低速段最大位置(+1)，点击下一步。
panelstrings.desc_en: 2. Step the pedal to the maximum position of the low speed section (+1) and click Next.

panelstrings.desc_zh: 3：将脚踏正踩到最大位置(+2)，点击下一步。
panelstrings.desc_en: 3. Step on the pedal to the maximum position (+2) and click Next.

panelstrings.desc_zh: 4：将脚踏反踩至反踩第一档(-1)，即抬压脚位置，点击下一步。
panelstrings.desc_en: 4. Step on the pedal to reverse the first gear (-1), that is, raise the pressure foot position, click Next.

panelstrings.desc_zh: 5：将脚踏反踩到底，即剪线位置(-2)，点击下一步。
panelstrings.desc_en: 5. Put the pedal back to the end, that is, the trimming position (-2), click Next.

panelstrings.desc_zh: 点击数字按钮，相应的电磁铁或电磁阀会动作，注意安全！
panelstrings.desc_en: Click the number button, the solenoid or actuator will action. Be careful of saftey!

panelstrings.desc_zh: 请输入密码获取技术员权限！
panelstrings.desc_en: Please type the password to get authority!

panelstrings.desc_zh: 请输入旧的密码获取权限设置新密码！
panelstrings.desc_en: Please type the old password to reset the password!

panelstrings.desc_zh: 旧密码输入正确,请输入新密码！
panelstrings.desc_en: Old password is passed, input the new password!

panelstrings.desc_zh: 如果段数为奇数，则一定由倒缝开始，且倒缝针数等于反缝针数。
panelstrings.desc_en: If sections number is odd, the sewing begins backward, the forward stitches is same as backward.

panelstrings.desc_zh: 0：无功能;1：倒缝;2：正缝补针;3：倒缝补针;4：停车时正缝补针，运行时倒缝;5：停车时倒缝补针，运行时倒缝;6：压脚交互量;7：快捷取消前后加固;8：大小针距;9：额外的面线张力;10：暂停模式;11：穿线模式;12：缝线中心导向;13：倾倒开关;14：面线检测传感器;15：护指板检测报警;16：旋梭盖板检测报警;17：按键切换压脚状态;18：膝控压脚开关;
panelstrings.desc_en: 0. no function;1. reverse sewing direction;2. Correction with forward stitches;3. Correction with backward stitches;4. 2 when stopped, 1 when sewing;5. 3 when stopped, 1 when sewing;6. Switch the stroke height;7. Toggle tacking function;8. Switch the stitch length;9. Additional tension;10. Toggle tacking function;11. Thread a needle;12. Seam center guide;13. Tilt detection;14. Upper thread broken detect sensor;15. Finger protection detect sensor;16. Hook cover opening detect sensor;17. Lift or release the foot;18. Knee switch;

panelstrings.desc_zh: 0：无功能;1：剪线;2：松线;3：夹线;4：倒缝;5：抬压脚;6：交互量;7：第二夹线器;8：扫线;9：第二针距;10：机针冷却;11：短线头额外剪线器;12：缝线中心导向;13：短线头零针距
panelstrings.desc_en: 0. No function;1. Trimmer;2. Tension;3. Clamp;4. Reverse;5. Foot lift;6. Stroke height;7. Additional tension;8. Wiper;9. Second stitch length;10. Needle cooling;11. Second trimmer for short trim;12. Seam center guide;13. Second stitch length for short trim;
